data.description: This Bluffs 3 bedroom home with amazing curb appeal is situated on a cul-de-sac. Gorgeous landscaping with roses and an automatic sprinkler system to keep them blooming. As a bonus, the solar panels provide a huge utility savings! The large living area is stunning with vaulted ceilings, hardwood floors, and large windows offering lots of natural light. The kitchen features a 10' island with solid wood custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances, granite counters, and a large pantry. The master bedroom features an all tile shower, a free standing soaking tub, and double sinks, along with an amazing walk-in closet (make sure you look behind the door!). French doors in the master lead to a side yard and a private patio. The property extends beyond the back fence, has great views of Bluffs green-spaces, and the owner has built a beautiful stone patio on the hill. Take a look by going up the small hill at the left of the home, outside the fence.  Current loan is assumable at 2.875 interest!
